    <div id="object-orientated-software-design-finals">
        <h2>Object Orientated Software Design Finals</h2>
        <img src="/images/OOSD-Finals-Terminal.png" alt="Object Orientated Software Design Finals">
        <br>
        <p>
            A drink stock manager plus POS system command line interface java program. It allows the user 
            to register as either an admin or regular user. Depending on the level chosen, the user will 
            have access to editing suppliers, customers and stock information. Other than that, depending 
            on the level access, the user can add suppliers, customers stock of different categories, remove 
            them, edit them, buy from suppliers, sell to customers and edit the user's information.
            <br><br>
            Languages Used:
            <li>Java</li>
        </p>
        <br>
        <p>
            Features of the Program:
            <li>Buy from Supplier</li>
            <li>Check Wallet & Profit and Loss</li>
            <li>Create Supplier/Customer/Stock</li>
            <li>Edit Supplier/Customer/Stock</li>
            <li>Manage Stock Lists</li>
            <li>Register/Login</li>
            <li>Sell to Customer</li>
        </p>
