            It was started on the 6<sup>th</sup> November, 2022. And I will be honest right now. Although I had a plan,
            content and a layout in mind, it was not a concrete design. So, I encountered a number of road bumps.
            However, at the randomest of times, designs come into my head. And eventually I reached here.<br>
            Currently the site is being created with the help of the Javascript Framework called Astro. I originally 
            coded it the old fashion way in Visual Studio Code. That was until a good friend of mine introduced me to 
            Astro. It was what I hoped the future of programming would be. Different languages and frameworks combined 
            into one. Instead of there being millions of different langauges or frameworks out there. Well, technically 
